#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:145
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ubuntu Linux"
msgstr "Ubuntu Linux"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:149
msgid ""
"If you want to have the option of creating replicated storage using DRBD, you will need to install _drbd-dkms_ and _drbd-utils_. These packages will need to be installed on all "
"nodes. You will also need to choose a volume manager, either ZFS or LVM, in this instance we're using LVM."
msgstr "如果您想选择使用DRBD创建复制存储，则需要安装 _drbd-dkms_ 和  _drbd-utils_ 。这些包需要安装在所有节点上。您还需要选择一个卷管理器，ZFS或LVM，在本例中我们使用的是LVM。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:152
#, no-wrap
msgid "# apt install -y drbd-dkms drbd-utils lvm2\n"
msgstr "# apt install -y drbd-dkms drbd-utils lvm2\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:155 administration-linstor.adoc:189 administration-linstor.adoc:219
msgid ""
"Depending on whether your node is a LINSTOR controller, satellite, or both (Combined) will determine what packages are required on that node. For combined type nodes, we'll "
"need both the controller and satellite LINSTOR package."
msgstr "根据节点是LINSTOR controller、satellite还是两者（组合）将确定该节点上需要哪些包。对于组合型节点，我们需要controller和satellite 的LINSTOR包。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:157 administration-linstor.adoc:191 administration-linstor.adoc:223
msgid "Combined node:"
msgstr "组合节点："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "# apt install linstor-controller linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"
msgstr "# apt install linstor-controller linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:163 administration-linstor.adoc:197 administration-linstor.adoc:229
msgid "That will make our remaining nodes our Satellites, so we'll need to install the following packages on them:"
msgstr "这将使我们剩余的节点成为我们的Satellites，因此我们需要在它们上安装以下软件包："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "# apt install linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"
msgstr "# apt install linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:170
#, no-wrap
msgid "SUSE Linux Enterprise Server"
msgstr "SUSE Linux企业服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:174
msgid "SLES High Availability Extension (HAE) includes DRBD."
msgstr "SLES高可用性扩展（HAE）包括DRBD。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:177
msgid "On SLES, DRBD is normally installed via the software installation component of YaST2. It comes bundled with the High Availabilty package selection."
msgstr "在SLES上，DRBD通常通过YaST2的软件安装组件安装。它与高可用性软件包捆绑在一起。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:180
msgid ""
"As we download DRBD's newest module we can check if the LVM-tools are up to date as well. User who prefer a command line install may simply issue the following command to get "
"the newest DRBD and LVM version:"
msgstr "当我们下载DRBD的最新模块时，我们可以检查LVM工具是否也是最新的。喜欢命令行安装的用户可用以下命令获得最新的DRBD和LVM版本："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:183
#, no-wrap
msgid "# zypper install drbd lvm2\n"
msgstr "# zypper install drbd lvm2\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:194
#, no-wrap
msgid "# zypper install linstor-controller linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"
msgstr "# zypper install linstor-controller linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:200
#, no-wrap
msgid "# zypper install linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"
msgstr "# zypper install linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:204
#, no-wrap
msgid "CentOS"
msgstr "CentOS"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:209
msgid ""
"CentOS has had DRBD 8 since release 5. For DRBD 9 you'll need to look at EPEL and similar sources.  Alternatively, if you have an active support contract with LINBIT you can "
"utilize our RHEL 8 repositories.  DRBD can be installed using `yum`. We can also check for the newest version of the LVM-tools as well."
msgstr ""
"CentOS从第5版开始就有了DRBD 8。对于DRBD 9，您需要查看EPEL和类似的源代码。或者，如果您与LINBIT有签订支持合同，您可以利用我们的RHEL 8存储库。可以使用 `yum` 安装DRBD。我们也可以检"
"查最新版本的LVM工具。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:212
msgid "LINSTOR *requires* DRBD 9 if you wish to have replicated storage. This requires an external repository to be configured, either LINBIT's or a 3rd parties."
msgstr "如果要复制存储，LINSTOR *需要* DRBD 9。这需要配置外部存储库，可以是LINBIT的，也可以是第三方的。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:215
#, no-wrap
msgid "# yum install drbd kmod-drbd lvm2\n"
msgstr "# yum install drbd kmod-drbd lvm2\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:221
msgid "On RHEL 8 systems you will need to install python2 for the linstor-client to work."
msgstr "在RHEL8系统上，需要安装python2才能让linstor客户端工作。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:226
#, no-wrap
msgid "# yum install linstor-controller linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"
msgstr "# yum install linstor-controller linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:232
#, no-wrap
msgid "# yum install linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"
msgstr "# yum install linstor-satellite  linstor-client\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:236
#, no-wrap
msgid "Upgrading"
msgstr "升级"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:242
msgid ""
"LINSTOR doesn't support rolling upgrade, controller and satellites must have the same version, otherwise the controller with discard the satellite with a `VERSION_MISMATCH`.  "
"But this isn't a problem, as the satellite won't do any actions as long it isn't connected to a controller and DRBD will not be disrupted by any means."
msgstr ""
"LINSTOR不支持滚动升级，controller和satellites必须具有相同的版本，否则controller将丢弃具有 `版本不匹配` 的satellite。但这不是问题，因为satellite不会做任何动作，只要它没有连接到"
"controller，DRBD就不会被任何方式中断。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:248
msgid ""
"If you are using the embedded default H2 database and the linstor-controller package is upgraded an automatic backup file of the database will be created in the default `/var/"
"lib/linstor` directory.  This file is a good restore point if for any reason a linstor-controller database migration should fail, than it is recommended to report the error to "
"Linbit and restore the old database file and downgrade to your previous controller version."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用的是嵌入的H2数据库，并且升级了linstor-controller包，那么将在默认的 `/var/lib/linstor` 目录中创建数据库的自动备份文件。如果由于任何原因linstor-controller数据库迁移失"
"败，则此文件是一个很好的还原点，建议将错误报告给Linbit并还原旧的数据库文件并降级到以前的controller版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:251
msgid "If you use any external database or etcd, it is recommended to do a manually backup of your current database to have a restore point."
msgstr "如果使用任何外部数据库或etcd，建议手动备份当前数据库以获得还原点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:256
msgid ""
"So first upgrade the `linstor-controller`, `linstor-client` package on you controller host and restart the `linstor-controller`, the controller should start and all of it's "
"client should show `OFFLINE(VERSION_MISMATCH)`.  After that you can continue upgrading `linstor-satellite` on all satellite nodes and restart them, after a short reconnection "
"time they should all show `ONLINE` again and your upgrade is finished."
msgstr ""
"因此，首先升级controller主机上的 `linstor-controller` 和 `linstor-client` 包，然后重新启动 `linstor-controler`, controller应启动，其所有客户端应显示 `OFFLINE（VERSION_MISMATCH）"
"`。之后，您可以继续升级所有卫星节点上的`linstor-satellite`, 并重新启动它们，在短时间重新连接后，它们都应再次显示 `ONLINE`，并且您的升级已完成。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:259
#, no-wrap
msgid "Containers"
msgstr "容器"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:263
msgid "LINSTOR is also available as containers. The base images are available in LINBIT's container registry, `drbd.io`."
msgstr "LINSTOR也可用容器运行。基础镜像可以在LINBIT的容器registry仓库 `drbd.io` 中找到。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:266
msgid "In order to access the images, you first have to login to the registry (reach out to sales@linbit.com for credentials):"
msgstr "要访问这些镜像，首先必须登录registry（访问sales@linbit.com获取凭据）："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:269
#, no-wrap
msgid "# docker login drbd.io\n"
msgstr "# docker login drbd.io\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:272
msgid "The containers available in this repo are:"
msgstr "此repo中可用的容器包括："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:274
msgid "drbd.io/drbd9:rhel8"
msgstr "drbd.io/drbd9:rhel8"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:275
msgid "drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7"
msgstr "drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:276
msgid "drbd.io/drbd9:bionic"
msgstr "drbd.io/drbd9:bionic"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:277
msgid "drbd.io/linstor-csi"
msgstr "drbd.io/linstor-csi"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:278
msgid "drbd.io/linstor-controller"
msgstr "drbd.io/linstor-controller"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:279
msgid "drbd.io/linstor-satellite"
msgstr "drbd.io/linstor-satellite"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:280
msgid "drbd.io/linstor-client"
msgstr "drbd.io/linstor-client"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:283
msgid ""
"An up to date list of available images with versions can be retrieved by opening http://drbd.io in your browser. Make sure to access the host via \"http\", as the registry's "
"images themselves are served via \"https\"."
msgstr "通过在浏览器中打开http://drbd.io，可以可用image的最新列表。确保通过 \"http\"访问主机，因为registry的image本身通过 \"https\"提供服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:289
msgid ""
"To load the kernel module, needed only for LINSTOR satellites, you'll need to run a `drbd9` container in privileged mode. The kernel module containers either retrieve an "
"official LINBIT package from a customer repository, or they try to build the kernel modules from source. If you intend to build from source, you need to have the according "
"kernel headers (e.g., `kernel-devel`) installed on the host. There are 3 ways to execute such a module load container:"
msgstr ""
"要加载仅用于LINSTOR satellites 的内核模块，需要在特权模式下运行 `drbd9` 容器。内核模块容器要么从客户存储库中检索正式的LINBIT包，要么尝试从源代码构建内核模块。如果要从源代码构"
"建，则需要在主机上安装相应的内核头文件（例如， `kernel-devel`) 。执行这样的模块加载容器有三种方法："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:291
msgid "Specifying a LINBIT node hash and a distribution."
msgstr "指定LINBIT节点哈希和容器版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:292
msgid "Bind-mounting an existing repository configuration."
msgstr "绑定装入现有仓库配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:293
msgid "Not doing one of the above to trigger a build from source."
msgstr "不执行上述操作之一, 直接从源代码触发生成。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:295
msgid "Example using a hash and a distribution:"
msgstr "使用哈希和容器版本的示例："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:300
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -e LB_DIST=rhel7.7 -e LB_HASH=ThisIsMyNodeHash \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7\n"
msgstr ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -e LB_DIST=rhel7.7 -e LB_HASH=ThisIsMyNodeHash \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:303
msgid "Example using an existing repo config."
msgstr "使用现有repo配置的示例。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:308
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -v /etc/yum.repos.d/linbit.repo:/etc/yum.repos.d/linbit.repo:ro \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7\n"
msgstr ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -v /etc/yum.repos.d/linbit.repo:/etc/yum.repos.d/linbit.repo:ro \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:312
msgid ""
"In both cases (hash + distribution, as well as bind-mounting) the hash or config has to be from a node that has a special property set. Feel free to contact our support, and we "
"set this property."
msgstr "在这两种情况下（哈系+版本以及绑定挂载），哈系或配置必须来自具有特殊属性集的节点。请随时与我们的支持联系，我们将设置此属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:314
msgid "Example building from shipped source (RHEL based):"
msgstr "从已分发代码生成的示例（基于RHEL）："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:319
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -v /usr/src:/usr/src:ro \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7\n"
msgstr ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -v /usr/src:/usr/src:ro \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:rhel7\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:322
msgid "Example building from shipped source (Debian based):"
msgstr "从已发代码构建的示例（基于Debian）："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:327
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -v /usr/src:/usr/src:ro -v /usr/lib:/usr/lib:ro \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:bionic\n"
msgstr ""
"# docker run -it --rm --privileged -v /lib/modules:/lib/modules \\\n"
"  -v /usr/src:/usr/src:ro -v /usr/lib:/usr/lib:ro \\\n"
"  drbd.io/drbd9:bionic\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:331
msgid "Do *not* bind-mount `/usr/lib` on RHEL based systems! And do *not* forget to bind-mount it on Debian based ones."
msgstr "*不要* bind-mount `/usr/lib` 到基于RHEL的系统上！也不要把它bind-mount到基于Debian的系统上。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:338
msgid ""
"For now (i.e., pre DRBD 9 version \"9.0.17\"), you must use the containerized DRBD kernel module, as opposed to loading a kernel module onto the host system. If you intend to "
"use the containers you should not install the DRBD kernel module on your host systems. For DRBD version 9.0.17 or greater, you can install the kernel module as usual on the "
"host system, but you need to make sure to load the module with the `usermode_helper=disabled` parameter (e.g., `modprobe drbd usermode_helper=disabled`)."
msgstr ""
"到现在为止（即，DRBD 9之前的版本 \\9.0.17\"），您必须使用容器化DRBD内核模块，而不是将内核模块加载到主机系统上。如果要使用容器，则不应在主机系统上安装DRBD内核模块。对于DRBD版本"
"9.0.17或更高版本，可以像往常一样在主机系统上安装内核模块，但需要确保使用  `usermode_helper=disabled`参数（例如， `modprobe drbd usermode_helper=disabled` ）加载模块。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:340
msgid "Then run the LINSTOR satellite container, also privileged, as a daemon:"
msgstr "然后以守护进程的身份运行LINSTOR satellite容器, 也需具有特权："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:343
#, no-wrap
msgid "# docker run -d --name=linstor-satellite --net=host -v /dev:/dev --privileged drbd.io/linstor-satellite\n"
msgstr "# docker run -d --name=linstor-satellite --net=host -v /dev:/dev --privileged drbd.io/linstor-satellite\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:347
msgid "`net=host` is required for the containerized `drbd-utils` to be able to communicate with the host-kernel via netlink."
msgstr "`net=host` 是容器化的 `drbd-utils` 通过netlink与主机内核通信所必需的。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:350
msgid "To run the LINSTOR controller container as a daemon, mapping ports `3370`, `3376` and `3377` on the host to the container:"
msgstr "要将LINSTOR控制器容器作为守护进程运行，请将主机上的端口 `3370` 、 `3376` 和 `3377` 映射到该容器："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:353
#, no-wrap
msgid "# docker run -d --name=linstor-controller -p 3370:3370 -p 3376:3376 -p 3377:3377 drbd.io/linstor-controller\n"
msgstr "# docker run -d --name=linstor-controller -p 3370:3370 -p 3376:3376 -p 3377:3377 drbd.io/linstor-controller\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:358
msgid ""
"To interact with the containerized LINSTOR cluster, you can either use a LINSTOR client installed on a system via packages, or via the containerized LINSTOR client. To use the "
"LINSTOR client container:"
msgstr "要与容器化LINSTOR集群交互，可以使用通过包安装在系统上的LINSTOR客户端，也可以通过容器化LINSTOR客户端。要使用LINSTOR客户端容器，请执行以下操作："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:361
#, no-wrap
msgid "# docker run -it --rm -e LS_CONTROLLERS=<controller-host-IP-address> drbd.io/linstor-client node list\n"
msgstr "# docker run -it --rm -e LS_CONTROLLERS=<controller-host-IP-address> drbd.io/linstor-client node list\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:366
msgid "From this point you would use the LINSTOR client to initialize your cluster and begin creating resources using the typical LINSTOR patterns."
msgstr "从这里开始，您可以使用LINSTOR客户端初始化集群，并开始使用典型的LINSTOR模式创建资源。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:368
msgid "To stop and remove a daemonized container and image:"
msgstr "要停止并删除守护的容器和映像，请执行以下操作："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:372
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# docker stop linstor-controller\n"
"# docker rm linstor-controller\n"
msgstr ""
"# docker stop linstor-controller\n"
"# docker rm linstor-controller\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:375
#, no-wrap
msgid "Initializing your cluster"
msgstr "初始化集群"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:377
msgid "We assume that the following steps are accomplished on *all* cluster nodes:"
msgstr "我们假设在 *所有* 集群节点上已完成以下步骤："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:379
msgid "The DRBD9 kernel module is installed and loaded"
msgstr "DRBD9内核模块已安装并加载"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:380
msgid "`drbd-utils` are installed"
msgstr "已安装 `drbd-utils`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:381
msgid "`LVM` tools are installed"
msgstr "`LVM` 工具已安装"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:382
msgid "`linstor-controller` and/or `linstor-satellite` its dependencies are installed"
msgstr "`linstor-controller` 和/或 `linstor-satellite` 的依赖项已安装"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:383
msgid "The `linstor-client` is installed on the `linstor-controller` node"
msgstr "`linstor-client` 已安装在 `linstor-controller` 节点上"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:385
msgid "Start and enable the linstor-controller service on the host where it has been installed:"
msgstr "在已安装linstor-controller的主机上启动并启用该服务："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:388
#, no-wrap
msgid "# systemctl enable --now linstor-controller\n"
msgstr "# systemctl enable --now linstor-controller\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:392
msgid "If you are sure the linstor-controller service gets automatically enabled on installation you can use the following command as well:"
msgstr "如果您确定linstor控制器服务在安装时自动启用，则还可以使用以下命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:395
#, no-wrap
msgid "# systemctl start linstor-controller\n"
msgstr "# systemctl start linstor-controller\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:398
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using the LINSTOR client"
msgstr "使用LINSTOR客户端"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:403
msgid ""
"Whenever you run the LINSTOR command line client, it needs to know where your linstor-controller runs. If you do not specify it, it will try to reach a locally running linstor-"
"controller listening on IP `127.0.0.1` port `3376`. Therefore we will use the `linstor-client` on the same host as the `linstor-controller`."
msgstr ""
"无论何时运行LINSTOR命令行客户端，它都需要知道listor-controller的运行位置。如果不指定它，它将尝试访问本地运行的linstor-controller，该控制器侦听IP `127.0.0.1` 端口是 `3376` 。这"
"样，我们可以在与 `linstor-controller` 相同的主机上使用 `linstor-client` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:406
msgid "The `linstor-satellite` requires ports 3366 and 3367. The `linstor-controller` requires ports 3376 and 3377. Make sure you have these ports allowed on your firewall."
msgstr "`linstor-satellite` 需要端口3366和3367。 `linstor-controller` 需要端口3376和3377。确保防火墙上允许这些端口。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:409
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor node list\n"
msgstr "# linstor node list\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:411
msgid "should give you an empty list and not an error message."
msgstr "应该输出一个空列表，而不是一条错误信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:416
msgid ""
"You can use the `linstor` command on any other machine, but then you need to tell the client how to find the linstor-controller. As shown, this can be specified as a command "
"line option, an environment variable, or in a global file:"
msgstr "您可以在任何其他机器上使用 `linstor` 命令，但随后您需要告诉客户端如何找到linstor-controller。如下所示，可以将其指定为命令行选项、环境变量或全局文件："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:420
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor --controllers=alice node list\n"
"# LS_CONTROLLERS=alice linstor node list\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor --controllers=alice node list\n"
"# LS_CONTROLLERS=alice linstor node list\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:424
msgid "Alternatively you can create the `/etc/linstor/linstor-client.conf` file and populate it like below."
msgstr "或者，您可以创建 `/etc/linstor/linstor-client.conf` 文件，并按如下方式填充它。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:429
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[global]\n"
"controllers=alice\n"
msgstr ""
"[global]\n"
"controllers=alice\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:434
msgid "If you have multiple linstor-controllers configured you can simply specify them all in a comma separated list. The linstor-client will simply try them in the order listed."
msgstr "如果配置了多个linstor控制器，只需在逗号分隔的列表中指定它们即可。linstor客户机会按照列出的顺序进行尝试。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:439
msgid ""
"The linstor-client commands can also be used in a much faster and convenient way by only writing the starting letters of the parameters e.g.: `linstor node list` -> `linstor n "
"l`"
msgstr "linstor-client命令也可以通过只写参数的起始字母来快速方便地使用，例如： `linstor node list` -> `linstor n l`"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:441
#, no-wrap
msgid "Adding nodes to your cluster"
msgstr "向集群添加节点"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:444
msgid "The next step is to add nodes to your LINSTOR cluster. You need to provide:"
msgstr "下一步是将节点添加到LINSTOR集群。您需要提供："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:446
msgid "A node name which *must* match the output of `uname -n`"
msgstr "一个节点名，*必须* 匹配 `uname -n` 的输出`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:447
msgid "The IP address of the node."
msgstr "节点的IP地址。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:450
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor node create bravo 10.43.70.3\n"
msgstr "# linstor node create bravo 10.43.70.3\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:455
msgid ""
"When you use `linstor node list` you will see that the new node is marked as offline. Now start and enable the linstor-satellite on that node so that the service comes up on "
"reboot as well:"
msgstr "使用 `linstor node list`时，将看到新节点标记为脱机。现在启动并启用该节点上的 linstor-satellite，以便服务在重新启动时也启动："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:457
#, no-wrap
msgid "# systemctl enable --now  linstor-satellite\n"
msgstr "# systemctl enable --now  linstor-satellite\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:462
msgid "You can also use `systemctl start linstor-satellite` if you are sure that the service is already enabled as default and comes up on reboot."
msgstr "如果您确定该服务已默认启用并在重新启动时启动，则还可以使用  `systemctl start linstor-satellite` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:466
msgid ""
"About 10 seconds later you will see the status in `linstor node list` becoming online. Of course the satellite process may be started before the controller knows about the "
"existence of the satellite node."
msgstr "大约10秒后，您将看到 `linstor node list` 中的状态变为联机。当然，在controller知道satellite节点的存在之前，satellite进程已经启动完毕。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:470
msgid "In case the node which hosts your controller should also contribute storage to the LINSTOR cluster, you have to add it as a node and start the linstor-satellite as well."
msgstr "如果承载controller的节点也应该为LINSTOR集群提供存储空间，则必须将其添加为节点并启动linstor-satellite。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:472
#, no-wrap
msgid "Storage pools"
msgstr "存储池"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:479
msgid ""
"<<StoragePool,StoragePools>> identify storage in the context of LINSTOR.  To group storage pools from multiple nodes, simply use the same name on each node.  For example, one "
"valid approach is to give all SSDs one name and all HDDs another."
msgstr ""
"<<StoragePool,StoragePools>>在LINSTOR上下文中用于标识存储。要对多个节点的存储池进行分组，只需在每个节点上使用相同的名称。例如，一种有效的方法是给所有的ssd取一个名字，给所有的hdd"
"取另一个名字。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:485
msgid ""
"On each host contributing storage, you need to create either an LVM VG or a ZFS zPool. The VGs and zPools identified with one LINSTOR storage pool name may have different VG or "
"zPool names on the hosts, but do yourself a favor and use the same VG or zPool name on all nodes."
msgstr ""
"在每个提供存储的主机上，您需要创建LVM VG或ZFS zPool。使用一个LINSTOR存储池名称标识的VG和zPool在主机上可能有不同的VG或zPool名称，但请您自己考虑，是否在所有节点上使用相同的VG或"
"zPool名称。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:488
#, no-wrap
msgid "# vgcreate vg_ssd /dev/nvme0n1 /dev/nvme1n1 [...]\n"
msgstr "# vgcreate vg_ssd /dev/nvme0n1 /dev/nvme1n1 [...]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:491
msgid "These then need to be registered with LINSTOR:"
msgstr "然后需要向LINSTOR注册："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:495
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor storage-pool create lvm alpha pool_ssd vg_ssd\n"
"# linstor storage-pool create lvm bravo pool_ssd vg_ssd\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor storage-pool create lvm alpha pool_ssd vg_ssd\n"
"# linstor storage-pool create lvm bravo pool_ssd vg_ssd\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:503
msgid ""
"The storage pool name and common metadata is referred to as a _storage pool definition_.  The listed commands create a storage pool definition implicitly.  You can see that by "
"using `linstor storage-pool-definition list`.  Creating storage pool definitions explicitly is possible but not necessary."
msgstr ""
"存储池名称和公共元数据称为 _存储池定义_ 。上面列出的命令隐式创建了存储池定义。使用 `linstor storage-pool-definition list` 可以看到这一点。也可以显式创建存储池定义，但不是必需"
"的。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:505
msgid "To list your storage-pools you can use:"
msgstr "要列出您可以使用的存储池，请执行以下操作："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:508
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor storage-pool list\n"
msgstr "# linstor storage-pool list\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:511 administration-linstor.adoc:526
msgid "or using the short version"
msgstr "或者使用短版本"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:514
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor sp l\n"
msgstr "# linstor sp l\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:520
msgid ""
"In case anything goes wrong with the storage pool's VG/zPool, e.g. the VG having been renamed or somehow became invalid you can delete the storage pool in LINSTOR with the "
"following command, given that only resources with all their volumes in the so-called 'lost' storage pool are attached. This feature is available since LINSTOR v0.9.13."
msgstr ""
"如果存储池的VG/zPool出现任何问题，例如VG已被重命名或以某种方式变得无效，您可以使用以下命令删除LINSTOR中的存储池，前提是只有资源及其所有卷都位于所谓的 `lost` 存储池中。此功能自"
"LINSTOR v0.9.13起可用。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:523
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor storage-pool lost alpha pool_ssd\n"
msgstr "# linstor storage-pool lost alpha pool_ssd\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:529
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor sp lo alpha pool_ssd\n"
msgstr "# linstor sp lo alpha pool_ssd\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:536
msgid ""
"Should the deletion of the storage pool be prevented due to attached resources or snapshots with some of its volumes in another still functional storage pool, hints will be "
"given in the 'status' column of the corresponding list-command (e.g. `linstor resource list`). After deleting the LINSTOR-objects in the lost storage pool manually, the lost-"
"command can be executed again to ensure a complete deletion of the storage pool and its remaining objects."
msgstr ""
"如果由于附加的资源或快照（其中一些卷位于另一个仍在运行的存储池中）而阻止删除存储池，则会在相应list命令的 `status` 列中给出提示（例如 `linstor resource list` )   手动删除丢失的存"
"储池中的LINSTOR对象后，可以再次执行lost命令，以确保完全删除了存储池及其剩余对象。"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:538
#, no-wrap
msgid "A storage pool per backend device"
msgstr "每个后端设备的存储池"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:544
msgid ""
"In clusters where you have only one kind of storage and the capability to hot-repair storage devices, you may choose a model where you create one storage pool per physical "
"backing device. The advantage of this model is to confine failure domains to a single storage device."
msgstr "在仅只有一种存储和热修复存储设备功能的集群中，可以选择一种模型，在该模型中为每个物理备份设备创建一个存储池。此模型的优点是将故障域限制在单个存储设备上。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:546
#, no-wrap
msgid "Resource groups"
msgstr "资源组"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:553
msgid ""
"A resource group is a parent object of a resource definition where all property changes made on a resource group will be inherited by it's resource definition children. The "
"resource group also stores settings for automatic placement rules and can spawn a resource definition depending on the stored rules."
msgstr "资源组是资源定义的父对象，其中对资源组所做的所有属性更改都将由其资源定义的子级继承。资源组还存储自动放置规则的设置，并可以根据存储的规则生成资源定义。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:558
msgid ""
"In simpler terms, resource groups are like templates that define characteristics of resources created from them. Changes to these pseudo templates will be applied to all "
"resources that were created from the resource group, retroactively."
msgstr "简单地说，资源组就像模板，定义从它们创建的资源的特性。对这些伪模板的更改将应用于从资源组中创建的所有资源，并具有追溯性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:564
msgid ""
"Using resource groups to define how you'd like your resources provisioned should be considered the de facto method for deploying volumes provisioned by LINSTOR. Chapters that "
"follow which describe creating each _resource_ from a _resource-definition_ and _volume-definition_ should only be used in special scenarios."
msgstr "使用资源组定义资源配置方式应被视为部署由LINSTOR配置的卷的典型方法。后面描述从 _资源定义_ 和 _卷定义_ 创建每个 _资源_ 的章节应仅在特殊情况下使用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:569
msgid ""
"Even if you choose not to create and use _resource-groups_ in your LINSTOR cluster, all resources created from _resource-definitions_ and _volume-definitions_ will exist in the "
"'DfltRscGrp' _resource-group_."
msgstr "即使您选择不在LINSTOR集群中创建和使用 _资源组_ ，从 _资源定义_ 和 _卷定义_ 创建的所有资源都将存在于 `DfltRscGrp`  _资源组_ 中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:572
msgid "A simple pattern for deploying resources using resource groups would look like this:"
msgstr "使用资源组部署资源的简单模式如下："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:577
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource-group create my_ssd_group --storage-pool pool_ssd --place-count 2\n"
"# linstor volume-group create my_ssd_group\n"
"# linstor resource-group spawn-resources my_ssd_group my_ssd_res 20G\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource-group create my_ssd_group --storage-pool pool_ssd --place-count 2\n"
"# linstor volume-group create my_ssd_group\n"
"# linstor resource-group spawn-resources my_ssd_group my_ssd_res 20G\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:582
msgid ""
"The commands above would result in a resource named 'my_ssd_res' with a 20GB volume replicated twice being automatically provisioned from nodes who participate in the storage "
"pool named 'pool_ssd'."
msgstr "上述命令创建出一个名为 `my_ssd_res` 的资源，其中一个定义了双副本数的20GB卷将从名为 `pool_ssd` 的存储池的节点自动配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:589
msgid ""
"A more useful pattern could be to create a resource group with settings you've determined are optimal for your use case. Perhaps you have to run nightly online verifications of "
"your volumes' consistency, in that case, you could create a resource group with the 'verify-alg' of your choice already set so that resources spawned from the group are pre-"
"configured with 'verify-alg' set:"
msgstr ""
"一个更有用的模式可能是创建一个资源组，其中的设置是您确定的最适合您的用例的。也许您必须对卷的一致性进行夜间联机验证，在这种情况下，您可以创建一个资源组，其中已经设置了您选择的 "
"`verify-alg`  ，以便从该组生成的资源预先配置为 `verify-alg` 集："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:597
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource-group create my_verify_group --storage-pool pool_ssd --place-count 2\n"
"# linstor resource-group drbd-options --verify-alg crc32c my_verify_group\n"
"# linstor volume-group create my_verify_group\n"
"# for i in {00..19}; do\n"
"    linstor resource-group spawn-resources my_verify_group res$i 10G\n"
"  done\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource-group create my_verify_group --storage-pool pool_ssd --place-count 2\n"
"# linstor resource-group drbd-options --verify-alg crc32c my_verify_group\n"
"# linstor volume-group create my_verify_group\n"
"# for i in {00..19}; do\n"
"    linstor resource-group spawn-resources my_verify_group res$i 10G\n"
"  done\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:601
msgid "The commands above result in twenty 10GiB resources being created each with the 'crc32c' 'verify-alg' pre-configured."
msgstr "上述命令创建出20个10GiB资源，每个资源都预先配置了 `crc32c` 和 `verify alg`。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:608
msgid ""
"You can tune the settings of individual resources or volumes spawned from resource groups by setting options on the respective _resource-definition_ or _volume-definition_. For "
"example, if 'res11' from the example above is used by a very active database receiving lots of small random writes, you might want to increase the 'al-extents' for that "
"specific resource:"
msgstr ""
"您可以通过在相应的 _资源定义_ 或 _卷定义_ 上设置选项来优化从资源组派生的单个资源或卷的设置。例如，如果上面示例中的 `res11` 被一个接收大量小的随机写入的、非常活跃的数据库使用，则"
"可能需要增加该特定资源的 `al-extents` :"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:611
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor resource-definition drbd-options --al-extents 6007 res11\n"
msgstr "# linstor resource-definition drbd-options --al-extents 6007 res11\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:620
msgid ""
"If you configure a setting in a _resource-definition_ that is already configured on the _resource-group_ it was spawned from, the value set in the _resource-definition_ will "
"override the value set on the parent _resource-group_. For example, if the same 'res11' was required to use the slower but more secure 'sha256' hash algorithm in it's "
"verifications, setting the 'verify-alg' on the _resource-definition_ for 'res11' would override the value set on the _resource-group_:"
msgstr ""
"如果在 _资源定义_ 中配置的设置已在其派生的 _资源组_ 上配置，则 _资源定义_ 中设置的值将覆盖父 _资源组_ 上设置的值。例如，如果要求相同的 `res11` 在其验证中使用较慢但更安全的 "
"`sha256` 哈希算法，则在 `res11` 的 _资源定义_ 上设置的 `verify-alg` 值将覆盖其在 _资源组_ 中设置的值:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:623
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor resource-definition drbd-options --verify-alg sha256 res11\n"
msgstr "# linstor resource-definition drbd-options --verify-alg sha256 res11\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:630
msgid ""
"A rule of thumb for the hierarchy in which settings are inherited is the value \"closer\" to the resource or volume wins: _volume-definition_ settings take precedence over "
"_volume-group_ settings, and _resource-definition_ settings take precedence over _resource-group_ settings."
msgstr "继承设置的层次结构的一个经验法则是 \"更接近\" 资源或卷的值: _卷定义_ 设置优先于 _卷组_ 设置， _资源定义_ 设置优先于 _资源组_ 设置。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:633
#, no-wrap
msgid "Cluster configuration"
msgstr "集群配置"

