msgid "LINSTOR can handle transparent encryption of drbd volumes. dm-crypt is used to encrypt the provided storage from the storage device."
msgstr "LINSTOR可以处理drbd卷的透明加密。dm-crypt用于对存储设备中提供的存储进行加密。"

