#: administration-linstor.adoc:1032
msgid "Add `luks` to the layer-list"
msgstr "将 `luks` 添加到层列表"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1033
msgid "Don't forget to re-enter the master passphrase after a controller restart."
msgstr "不要忘记在controller重新启动后重新输入主密码。"

