#: administration-linstor.adoc:1038
msgid "Disabling the user security on the `Linstor` controller is a one time operation and is afterwards persisted."
msgstr "在 `Linstor` controller上禁用用户安全性是一次操作，之后会被持久化。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1040
msgid "Stop the running linstor-controller via systemd: `systemctl stop linstor-controller`"
msgstr "通过 `systemctl stop linstor-controller` 停止正在运行的linstor控制器`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1041
msgid "Start a linstor-controller in debug mode: `/usr/share/linstor-server/bin/Controller -c /etc/linstor -d`"
msgstr "在调试模式下启动linstor控制器： `/usr/share/linstor-server/bin/Controller -c /etc/linstor -d`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1042
msgid "In the debug console enter: `setSecLvl secLvl(NO_SECURITY)`"
msgstr "在调试控制台中输入：`setSecLvl secLvl(NO_SECURITY)`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1043
msgid "Stop linstor-controller with the debug shutdown command: `shutdown`"
msgstr "使用调试关闭命令停止linstor控制器： `shutdown`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1044
msgid "Start the controller again with systemd: `systemctl start linstor-controller`"
msgstr "使用systemd重新启动控制器：`systemctl start linstor-controller`"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1046
#, no-wrap
msgid "Encrypt commands"
msgstr "加密命令"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1048
msgid "Below are details about the commands."
msgstr "下面是有关命令的详细信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1051
msgid "Before LINSTOR can encrypt any volume a master passphrase needs to be created.  This can be done with the linstor-client."
msgstr "在LINSTOR可以加密任何卷之前，需要创建主密码。这可以通过linstor客户端完成。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1054
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor encryption create-passphrase\n"
msgstr "# linstor encryption create-passphrase\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1058
msgid "`crypt-create-passphrase` will wait for the user to input the initial master passphrase (as all other crypt commands will with no arguments)."
msgstr "`crypt create-passphrase`将等待用户输入初始主密码（因为所有其他crypt命令都没有参数）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1060
msgid "If you ever want to change the master passphrase this can be done with:"
msgstr "如果您想更改主密码，可以使用以下方法："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1063
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor encryption modify-passphrase\n"
msgstr "# linstor encryption modify-passphrase\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1068
msgid ""
"The `luks` layer can be added when creating the resource-definition or the resource itself, whereas the former method is recommended since it will be automatically applied to "
"all resource created from that resource-definition."
msgstr "`luks` 层可以在创建资源定义或资源本身时添加，而建议使用前一种方法，因为它将自动应用于从该资源定义创建的所有资源。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1071
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor resource-definition create crypt_rsc --layer-list luks,storage\n"
msgstr "# linstor resource-definition create crypt_rsc --layer-list luks,storage\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1074
msgid "To enter the master passphrase (after controller restart) use the following command:"
msgstr "要输入主密码（在controller重新启动后），请使用以下命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1077
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor encryption enter-passphrase\n"
msgstr "# linstor encryption enter-passphrase\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1082
msgid ""
"Whenever the linstor-controller is restarted, the user has to send the master passphrase to the controller, otherwise LINSTOR is unable to reopen or create encrypted volumes."
msgstr "无论何时重新启动linstor controller，用户都必须向控制器发送主密码，否则linstor无法重新打开或创建加密卷。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1084
#, no-wrap
msgid "Checking the state of your cluster"
msgstr "检查集群状态"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1089
msgid ""
"LINSTOR provides various commands to check the state of your cluster.  These commands start with a 'list-' prefix and provide various filtering and sorting options. The '--"
"groupby' option can be used to group and sort the output in multiple dimensions."
msgstr "LINSTOR提供各种命令来检查集群的状态。这些命令以 `list-` 前缀开头，并提供各种筛选和排序选项。`--groupby` 选项可用于按多个维度对输出进行分组和排序。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1093
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor node list\n"
"# linstor storage-pool list --groupby Size\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor node list\n"
"# linstor storage-pool list --groupby Size\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1096
#, no-wrap
msgid "Managing snapshots"
msgstr "管理快照"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1098
msgid "Snapshots are supported with thin LVM and ZFS storage pools."
msgstr "精简LVM和ZFS存储池支持快照。"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1100
#, no-wrap
msgid "Creating a snapshot"
msgstr "创建快照"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1103
msgid "Assuming a resource definition named 'resource1' which has been placed on some nodes, a snapshot can be created as follows:"
msgstr "假设在某些节点上放置了名为 `resource1` 的资源定义，则可以按如下方式创建快照："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1106
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor snapshot create resource1 snap1\n"
msgstr "# linstor snapshot create resource1 snap1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1111
msgid "This will create snapshots on all nodes where the resource is present.  LINSTOR will ensure that consistent snapshots are taken even when the resource is in active use."
msgstr "这将在资源所在的所有节点上创建快照。LINSTOR将确保即使在资源处于活动使用状态时也创建一致的快照。"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1113
#, no-wrap
msgid "Restoring a snapshot"
msgstr "还原快照"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1117
msgid "The following steps restore a snapshot to a new resource.  This is possible even when the original resource has been removed from the nodes where the snapshots were taken."
msgstr "以下步骤将快照还原到新资源。即使原始资源已从创建快照的节点中删除，也可能发生这种情况。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1119
msgid "First define the new resource with volumes matching those from the snapshot:"
msgstr "首先使用与快照中的卷匹配的卷定义新资源："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1123
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource-definition create resource2\n"
"# linstor snapshot volume-definition restore --from-resource resource1 --from-snapshot snap1 --to-resource resource2\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource-definition create resource2\n"
"# linstor snapshot volume-definition restore --from-resource resource1 --from-snapshot snap1 --to-resource resource2\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1127
msgid "At this point, additional configuration can be applied if necessary.  Then, when ready, create resources based on the snapshots:"
msgstr "此时，如果需要，可以应用其他配置。然后，准备好后，根据快照创建资源："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1130
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor snapshot resource restore --from-resource resource1 --from-snapshot snap1 --to-resource resource2\n"
msgstr "# linstor snapshot resource restore --from-resource resource1 --from-snapshot snap1 --to-resource resource2\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1135
msgid ""
"This will place the new resource on all nodes where the snapshot is present.  The nodes on which to place the resource can also be selected explicitly; see the help (`linstor "
"snapshot resource restore -h`)."
msgstr "这将在快照所在的所有节点上放置新资源。也可以显式选择放置资源的节点；请参阅帮助（ `linstor snapshot resource restore -h` )."

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1137
#, no-wrap
msgid "Rolling back to a snapshot"
msgstr "回滚快照"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1143
msgid ""
"LINSTOR can roll a resource back to a snapshot state.  The resource must not be in use.  That is, it may not be mounted on any nodes.  If the resource is in use, consider "
"whether you can achieve your goal by <<s-restoring_a_snapshot-linstor,restoring the snapshot>> instead."
msgstr ""
"LINSTOR可以将资源回滚到快照状态。回滚时资源不能被使用。也就是说，它不能安装在任何节点上。如果资源正在使用中，请考虑是否可以通过<<s-restoring_a_snapshot-linstor,restoring the "
"snapshot>>来实现您的目标。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1145
msgid "Rollback is performed as follows:"
msgstr "回滚执行如下："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1148
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor snapshot rollback resource1 snap1\n"
msgstr "# linstor snapshot rollback resource1 snap1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1152
msgid "A resource can only be rolled back to the most recent snapshot.  To roll back to an older snapshot, first delete the intermediate snapshots."
msgstr "资源只能回滚到最近的快照。要回滚到旧快照，请首先删除中间快照。"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1154
#, no-wrap
msgid "Removing a snapshot"
msgstr "删除快照"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1156
msgid "An existing snapshot can be removed as follows:"
msgstr "可以按如下方式删除现有快照："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1159
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor snapshot delete resource1 snap1\n"
msgstr "# linstor snapshot delete resource1 snap1\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1162
#, no-wrap
msgid "Setting options for resources"
msgstr "设置资源选项"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1168
msgid ""
"DRBD options are set using LINSTOR commands.  Configuration in files such as `/etc/drbd.d/global_common.conf` that are not managed by LINSTOR will be ignored.  The following "
"commands show the usage and available options:"
msgstr "DRBD选项是使用LINSTOR命令设置的。将忽略诸如 `/etc/drbd.d/global_common.conf` 文件中未由LINSTOR管理的配置。以下命令显示用法和可用选项："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1174
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor controller drbd-options -h\n"
"# linstor resource-definition drbd-options -h\n"
"# linstor volume-definition drbd-options -h\n"
"# linstor resource drbd-peer-options -h\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor controller drbd-options -h\n"
"# linstor resource-definition drbd-options -h\n"
"# linstor volume-definition drbd-options -h\n"
"# linstor resource drbd-peer-options -h\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1178
msgid "For instance, it is easy to set the DRBD protocol for a resource named `backups`:"
msgstr "例如，很容易为名为 `backups` 的资源设置DRBD协议："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1181
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor resource-definition drbd-options --protocol C backups\n"
msgstr "# linstor resource-definition drbd-options --protocol C backups\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1184
#, no-wrap
msgid "Adding and removing disks"
msgstr "添加和删除磁盘"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1188
msgid "LINSTOR can convert resources between diskless and having a disk.  This is achieved with the `resource toggle-disk` command, which has syntax similar to `resource create`."
msgstr "LINSTOR可以在无盘和有盘之间转换资源。这是通过 `resource toggle disk` 命令实现的，该命令的语法类似于 `resource create` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1190
msgid "For instance, add a disk to the diskless resource `backups` on 'alpha':"
msgstr "例如，将磁盘添加到 `alpha` 上的无盘资源 `backups`："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1193
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor resource toggle-disk alpha backups --storage-pool pool_ssd\n"
msgstr "# linstor resource toggle-disk alpha backups --storage-pool pool_ssd\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1196
msgid "Remove this disk again:"
msgstr "再次删除此磁盘："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1199
#, no-wrap
msgid "# linstor resource toggle-disk alpha backups --diskless\n"
msgstr "# linstor resource toggle-disk alpha backups --diskless\n"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1202
#, no-wrap
msgid "Migrating disks"
msgstr "迁移磁盘"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1209
msgid ""
"In order to move a resource between nodes without reducing redundancy at any point, LINSTOR's disk migrate feature can be used.  First create a diskless resource on the target "
"node, and then add a disk using the `--migrate-from` option.  This will wait until the data has been synced to the new disk and then remove the source disk."
msgstr ""
"为了在节点之间移动资源而不减少任何点的冗余，可以使用LINSTOR的磁盘迁移功能。首先在目标节点上创建一个无盘资源，然后使用 `--migrate from` 选项添加一个磁盘。这将等到数据已同步到新磁"
"盘，然后删除源磁盘。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1211
msgid "For example, to migrate a resource `backups` from 'alpha' to 'bravo':"
msgstr "例如，要将资源 `backups` 从 `alpha` 迁移到 `bravo` ："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1215
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource create bravo backups --drbd-diskless\n"
"# linstor resource toggle-disk bravo backups --storage-pool pool_ssd --migrate-from alpha\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource create bravo backups --drbd-diskless\n"
"# linstor resource toggle-disk bravo backups --storage-pool pool_ssd --migrate-from alpha\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1218
#, no-wrap
msgid "DRBD Proxy with LINSTOR"
msgstr "LINSTOR的DRBD代理"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1223
msgid ""
"LINSTOR expects DRBD Proxy to be running on the nodes which are involved in the relevant connections. It does not currently support connections via DRBD Proxy on a separate "
"node."
msgstr "LINSTOR希望DRBD代理在相关连接所涉及的节点上运行。它目前不支持通过单独节点上的DRBD代理进行连接。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1228
msgid ""
"Suppose our cluster consists of nodes 'alpha' and 'bravo' in a local network and 'charlie' at a remote site, with a resource definition named `backups` deployed to each of the "
"nodes. Then DRBD Proxy can be enabled for the connections to 'charlie' as follows:"
msgstr ""
"假设我们的集群由本地网络中的节点 `alpha` 和 `bravo` 以及远程站点上的节点 `charlie` 组成，每个节点都部署了名为 `backups` 的资源定义。然后，可以为 `charlie` 的连接启用DRBD Proxy，"
"如下所示："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1232
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor drbd-proxy enable alpha charlie backups\n"
"# linstor drbd-proxy enable bravo charlie backups\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor drbd-proxy enable alpha charlie backups\n"
"# linstor drbd-proxy enable bravo charlie backups\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1235
msgid "The DRBD Proxy configuration can be tailored with commands such as:"
msgstr "DRBD代理配置可以通过以下命令定制："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1239
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor drbd-proxy options backups --memlimit 100000000\n"
"# linstor drbd-proxy compression zlib backups --level 9\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor drbd-proxy options backups --memlimit 100000000\n"
"# linstor drbd-proxy compression zlib backups --level 9\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1244
msgid ""
"LINSTOR does not automatically optimize the DRBD configuration for long-distance replication, so you will probably want to set some configuration options such as the protocol:"
msgstr "LINSTOR不会自动优化远程复制的DRBD配置，因此您可能需要设置一些配置选项，例如协议："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1248
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor resource-connection drbd-options alpha charlie backups --protocol A\n"
"# linstor resource-connection drbd-options bravo charlie backups --protocol A\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor resource-connection drbd-options alpha charlie backups --protocol A\n"
"# linstor resource-connection drbd-options bravo charlie backups --protocol A\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1251
msgid "Please contact LINBIT for assistance optimizing your configuration."
msgstr "请与LINBIT联系以获得优化配置的帮助。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1253
#, no-wrap
msgid "External database"
msgstr "外部数据库"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1257
msgid "It is possible to have LINSTOR working with an external database provider like Postgresql, MariaDB and since version 1.1.0 even ETCD key value store is supported."
msgstr "可以让LINSTOR与外部数据库提供程序（如Postgresql、MariaDB）一起工作，从版本1.1.0开始支持ETCD键值存储。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1261
msgid ""
"To use an external database there are a few additional steps to configure.  External-SQL database need to download their JDBC-driver and copy it to the lib folder, ETCD just "
"needs to correctly configure the LINSTOR."
msgstr "要使用外部数据库，还有几个额外的配置步骤。外部SQL数据库需要下载其JDBC驱动程序并将其复制到lib文件夹，ETCD只需要正确配置LINSTOR即可。"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1264
#, no-wrap
msgid "Postgresql"
msgstr "Postgresql"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1267
msgid "Postgresql JDBC driver can be downloaded here:"
msgstr "Postgresql JDBC驱动程序可以下载到："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1269
msgid "https://jdbc.postgresql.org/download.html"
msgstr "https://jdbc.postgresql.org/download.html"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1272 administration-linstor.adoc:1291
msgid "And afterwards copied to: `/usr/share/linstor-server/lib/`"
msgstr "然后复制到： `/usr/share/linstor server/lib/`"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1274
msgid "A sample Postgresql `linstor.toml` looks like this:"
msgstr "Postgresql `linstor.toml` 示例如下："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1280
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[db]\n"
"user = \"linstor\"\n"
"password = \"linstor\"\n"
"connection_url = \"jdbc:postgresql://localhost/linstor\"\n"
msgstr ""
"[db]\n"
"user = \"linstor\"\n"
"password = \"linstor\"\n"
"connection_url = \"jdbc:postgresql://localhost/linstor\"\n"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1283
#, no-wrap
msgid "MariaDB/Mysql"
msgstr "MariaDB/Mysql"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1286
msgid "MariaDB JDBC driver can be downloaded here:"
msgstr "MariaDB JDBC驱动程序可在以下位置下载："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1288
msgid "https://downloads.mariadb.org/connector-java/"
msgstr "https://downloads.mariadb.org/connector-java/"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1293
msgid "A sample MariaDB `linstor.toml` looks like this:"
msgstr "MariaDB `linstor.toml` 示例如下："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1299
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[db]\n"
"user = \"linstor\"\n"
"password = \"linstor\"\n"
"connection_url = \"jdbc:mariadb://localhost/LINSTOR?createDatabaseIfNotExist=true\"\n"
msgstr ""
"[db]\n"
"user = \"linstor\"\n"
"password = \"linstor\"\n"
"connection_url = \"jdbc:mariadb://localhost/LINSTOR?createDatabaseIfNotExist=true\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1303
msgid "The LINSTOR schema/database is created as `LINSTOR` so make sure the mariadb connection string refers to the `LINSTOR` schema, as in the example above."
msgstr "LINSTOR schema/数据库被创建为 `LINSTOR`，因此请确保mariadb连接字符串引用了 `LINSTOR` schema，如上面的示例所示。"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1306
#, no-wrap
msgid "ETCD"
msgstr "ETCD"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1310
msgid ""
"ETCD is a distributed key-value store that makes it easy to keep your LINSTOR database distributed in a HA-setup.  The ETCD driver is already included in the LINSTOR-controller "
"package and only needs to be configured in the `linstor.toml`."
msgstr "ETCD是一个分布式键值存储，它使得在HA设置中保持LINSTOR数据库的分布式变得容易。ETCD驱动程序已经包含在LINSTOR控制器包中，只需要在 `LINSTOR.toml` 中进行配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1312
msgid "More information on how to install and configure ETCD can be found here: https://etcd.io/docs[ETCD docs]"
msgstr "有关如何安装和配置ETCD的更多信息，请访问：https://etcd.io/docs[ETCD docs]"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1314
msgid "And here is a sample [db] section from the `linstor.toml`:"
msgstr "下面是 `linstor.toml` 中的[db]部分示例："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1320
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[db]\n"
"## only set user/password if you want to use authentication, only since LINSTOR 1.2.1\n"
"# user = \"linstor\"\n"
"# password = \"linstor\"\n"
msgstr ""
"[db]\n"
"## only set user/password if you want to use authentication, only since LINSTOR 1.2.1\n"
"# user = \"linstor\"\n"
"# password = \"linstor\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1324
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"## for etcd\n"
"## do not set user field if no authentication required\n"
"connection_url = \"etcd://etcdhost1:2379,etcdhost2:2379,etcdhost3:2379\"\n"
msgstr ""
"## for etcd\n"
"## do not set user field if no authentication required\n"
"connection_url = \"etcd://etcdhost1:2379,etcdhost2:2379,etcdhost3:2379\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1328
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"## if you want to use TLS, only since LINSTOR 1.2.1\n"
"# ca_certificate = \"ca.pem\"\n"
"# client_certificate = \"client.pem\"\n"
msgstr ""
"## if you want to use TLS, only since LINSTOR 1.2.1\n"
"# ca_certificate = \"ca.pem\"\n"
"# client_certificate = \"client.pem\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1333
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"## if you want to use client TLS authentication too, only since LINSTOR 1.2.1\n"
"# client_key_pkcs8_pem = \"client-key.pkcs8\"\n"
"## set client_key_password if private key has a password\n"
"# client_key_password = \"mysecret\"\n"
msgstr ""
"## if you want to use client TLS authentication too, only since LINSTOR 1.2.1\n"
"# client_key_pkcs8_pem = \"client-key.pkcs8\"\n"
"## set client_key_password if private key has a password\n"
"# client_key_password = \"mysecret\"\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1336
#, no-wrap
msgid "LINSTOR REST-API"
msgstr "LINSTOR REST-API"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1341
msgid ""
"To make LINSTOR's administrative tasks more accessible and also available for web-frontends a REST-API has been created. The REST-API is embedded in the linstor-controller and "
"since LINSTOR 0.9.13 configured via the the `linstor.toml` configuration file."
msgstr "为了使LINSTOR的管理任务更易于访问，并且也可用于web前端，创建了REST-API。REST-API嵌入到linstor controller中，从linstor 0.9.13开始通过 `linstor.toml` 配置文件配置。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1347
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[http]\n"
"  enabled = true\n"
"  port = 3370\n"
"  listen_addr = 127.0.0.1  # to disable remote access\n"
msgstr ""
"[http]\n"
"  enabled = true\n"
"  port = 3370\n"
"  listen_addr = 127.0.0.1  # to disable remote access\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1352
msgid "If you want to use the REST-API the current documentation can be found on the following link: https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis-docs/Linstor/Linstor/"
msgstr "如果您想使用REST-API，可以在以下链接中找到当前文档：https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis-docs/Linstor/Linstor/"

#. type: Title ====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1354
#, no-wrap
msgid "LINSTOR REST-API HTTPS"
msgstr "LINSTOR REST-API HTTPS"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1359
msgid ""
"The HTTP REST-API can also run secured by HTTPS and is highly recommended if you use any features that require authorization. Todo so you have to create a java keystore file "
"with a valid certificate that will be used to encrypt all HTTPS traffic."
msgstr "HTTP REST-API也可以通过HTTPS运行，如果您使用任何需要授权的功能，则强烈建议您使用它。所以你必须用一个有效的证书创建一个java密钥库文件，这个证书将用于加密所有的HTTPS通信。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1362
msgid "Here is a simple example on how you can create a self signed certificate with the `keytool` that is included in the java runtime:"
msgstr "下面是一个简单的示例，说明如何使用java运行时中包含的 `keytool` 创建自签名证书："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1367
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore ./keystore_linstor.jks\\\n"
" -alias linstor_controller\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=localhost, OU=SecureUnit, O=ExampleOrg, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"
msgstr ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore ./keystore_linstor.jks\\\n"
" -alias linstor_controller\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=localhost, OU=SecureUnit, O=ExampleOrg, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1372
msgid ""
"`keytool` will ask for a password to secure the generated keystore file and is needed for the LINSTOR-controller configuration.  In your `linstor.toml` file you have to add the "
"following section:"
msgstr "`keytool` 将要求密码来保护生成的密钥库文件，这是LINSTOR controller配置所需的。在 `linstor.toml` 文件中，必须添加以下部分："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1377
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[https]\n"
"  keystore = \"/path/to/keystore_linstor.jks\"\n"
"  keystore_password = \"linstor\"\n"
msgstr ""
"[https]\n"
"  keystore = \"/path/to/keystore_linstor.jks\"\n"
"  keystore_password = \"linstor\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1380
msgid "Now (re)start the `linstor-controller` and the HTTPS REST-API should be available on port 3371."
msgstr "现在（重新）启动 `linstor controller` ，端口3371上应该可以使用HTTPS REST-API。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1383
msgid "More information on how to import other certificates can be found here: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/tools/unix/keytool.html"
msgstr "有关如何导入其他证书的更多信息，请访问：https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/tools/unix/keytool.html"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1386
msgid "When HTTPS is enabled, all requests to the HTTP /v1/ REST-API will be redirected to the HTTPS redirect."
msgstr "当启用HTTPS时，对HTTP/v1/ REST-API的所有请求都将重定向到HTTPS重定向。"

#. type: Title =====
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1389
#, no-wrap
msgid "LINSTOR REST-API HTTPS restricted client access"
msgstr "LINSTOR REST-API HTTPS受限客户端访问"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1394
msgid ""
"Client access can be restricted by using a SSL truststore on the Controller.  Basically you create a certificate for your client and add it to your truststore and the client "
"then uses this certificate for authentication."
msgstr "可以通过在控制器上使用SSL信任库来限制客户端访问。基本上，您为您的客户机创建一个证书并将其添加到信任库中，然后客户机使用该证书进行身份验证。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1396
msgid "First create a client certificate:"
msgstr "首先创建客户端证书："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1402
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore client.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias client1\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Client Cert, OU=client, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"
msgstr ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore client.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias client1\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Client Cert, OU=client, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1405
msgid "Then we import this certificate to our controller truststore:"
msgstr "然后我们将此证书导入controller信任库："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1410
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore client.jks -destkeystore trustore_client.jks\n"
msgstr ""
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore client.jks -destkeystore trustore_client.jks\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1413
msgid "And enable the truststore in the `linstor.toml` configuration file:"
msgstr "并在 `linstor.toml` 配置文件中启用信任库："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1420
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[https]\n"
"  keystore = \"/path/to/keystore_linstor.jks\"\n"
"  keystore_password = \"linstor\"\n"
"  truststore = \"/path/to/trustore_client.jks\"\n"
"  truststore_password = \"linstor\"\n"
msgstr ""
"[https]\n"
"  keystore = \"/path/to/keystore_linstor.jks\"\n"
"  keystore_password = \"linstor\"\n"
"  truststore = \"/path/to/trustore_client.jks\"\n"
"  truststore_password = \"linstor\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1424
msgid "Now restart the Controller and it will no longer be possible to access the controller API without a correct certificate."
msgstr "现在重新启动controller，如果没有正确的证书，将无法再访问控制器API。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1427
msgid "The LINSTOR client needs the certificate in PEM format, so before we can use it we have to convert the java keystore certificate to the PEM format."
msgstr "LINSTOR客户机需要PEM格式的证书，因此在使用之前，我们必须将java密钥库证书转换为PEM格式。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1433
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Convert to pkcs12\n"
"keytool -importkeystore -srckeystore client.jks -destkeystore client.p12\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srcalias client1 -srcstoretype jks -deststoretype pkcs12\n"
msgstr ""
"# Convert to pkcs12\n"
"keytool -importkeystore -srckeystore client.jks -destkeystore client.p12\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srcalias client1 -srcstoretype jks -deststoretype pkcs12\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1436
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# use openssl to convert to PEM\n"
"openssl pkcs12 -in client.p12 -out client_with_pass.pem\n"
msgstr ""
"# use openssl to convert to PEM\n"
"openssl pkcs12 -in client.p12 -out client_with_pass.pem\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1439
msgid "To avoid entering the PEM file password all the time it might be convenient to remove the password."
msgstr "为了避免一直输入PEM文件密码，可以方便地删除密码。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1443
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"openssl rsa -in client_with_pass.pem -out client1.pem\n"
"openssl x509 -in client_with_pass.pem >> client1.pem\n"
msgstr ""
"openssl rsa -in client_with_pass.pem -out client1.pem\n"
"openssl x509 -in client_with_pass.pem >> client1.pem\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1446
msgid "Now this PEM file can easily be used in the client:"
msgstr "现在，这个PEM文件可以很容易地在客户端使用："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1449
#, no-wrap
msgid "linstor --certfile client1.pem node list\n"
msgstr "linstor --certfile client1.pem node list\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1454
msgid "The `--certfile` parameter can also added to the client configuration file, see <<s-using_the_linstor_client>> for more details."
msgstr "`--certfile` 参数也可以添加到客户端配置文件中，有关详细信息，请参见<<s-using_the_linstor_client>>。"

#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1457
#, no-wrap
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "Logging"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1463
msgid ""
"Linstor uses https://www.slf4j.org/[SLF4J] with https://logback.qos.ch/[Logback] as binding. This gives Linstor the possibilty to distinguish between the log levels `ERROR`, "
"`WARN`, `INFO`, `DEBUG` and `TRACE` (in order of increasing verbosity). In the current linstor version (1.1.2) the user has the following four methods to control the logging "
"level, ordered by priority (first has highest priority):"
msgstr ""
"Linstor使用 https://www.slf4j.org/[SLF4J] 和 https://logback.qos.ch/[Logback] 作为绑定。这使Linstor能够区分日志级别 `ERROR`、 `WARN` 、 `INFO` 、 `DEBUG` 和 `TRACE` （为了增加详"
"细程度）。在当前的linstor版本（1.1.2）中，用户有以下四种方法控制日志记录级别，按优先级排序（第一种方法具有最高优先级）："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1466
msgid "`TRACE` mode can be `enabled` or `disabled` using the debug console:"
msgstr "`TRACE` mode可以使用调试控制台, 通过 `enabled` 或 `disabled` 分别指明:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1471
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Command ==> SetTrcMode MODE(enabled)\n"
"SetTrcMode           Set TRACE level logging mode\n"
"New TRACE level logging mode: ENABLED\n"
msgstr ""
"Command ==> SetTrcMode MODE(enabled)\n"
"SetTrcMode           Set TRACE level logging mode\n"
"New TRACE level logging mode: ENABLED\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1474
msgid "When starting the controller or satellite a command line argument can be passed:"
msgstr "启动controller或satellite时，可以传递命令行参数："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1478
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"java ... com.linbit.linstor.core.Controller ... --log-level INFO\n"
"java ... com.linbit.linstor.core.Satellite  ... --log-level INFO\n"
msgstr ""
"java ... com.linbit.linstor.core.Controller ... --log-level INFO\n"
"java ... com.linbit.linstor.core.Satellite  ... --log-level INFO\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1481
msgid "The recommended place is the `logging` section in the `/etc/linstor/linstor.toml` file:"
msgstr "建议放在 `/etc/linstor/linstor.toml` 文件中的 `logging` 部分："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1485
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[logging]\n"
"   level=\"INFO\"\n"
msgstr ""
"[logging]\n"
"   level=\"INFO\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1490
msgid ""
"As Linstor is using Logback as an implementation, `/usr/share/linstor-server/lib/logback.xml` can also be used. Currently only this approach supports different log levels for "
"different components, like shown in the example below:"
msgstr "由于Linstor使用Logback作为实现，还可以使用 `/usr/share/Linstor server/lib/Logback.xml` 。目前只有这种方法支持不同组件的不同日志级别，如下例所示："

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1533
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
