#. type: Title ===
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1542
#, no-wrap
msgid "Secure Satellite connections"
msgstr "安全Satellite连接"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1549
msgid ""
"It is possible to have the LINSTOR use SSL secure TCP connection between controller and satellite connections.  Without going into further details on how java's SSL engine "
"works we will give you command line snippets using the `keytool` from java's runtime environment on how to configure a 3 node setup using secure connections.  The node setup "
"looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"可以让LINSTOR在controller和satellites连接之间使用SSL安全TCP连接。在不深入讨论java的SSL引擎如何工作的情况下，我们将向您提供使用java运行时环境中的 `keytool` 的命令行片段，介绍如何"
"使用安全连接配置3节点设置。节点设置如下所示："

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1552
msgid "Node `alpha` is the just the controller.  Node `bravo` and node `charlie` are just satellites."
msgstr "节点 `alpha` 只充当controller。节点 `bravo` 和节点 `charlie` 只充当卫星。"

#. type: Plain text
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1556
msgid "Here are the commands to generate such a keystore setup, values should of course be edited for your environment."
msgstr "下面是生成这样一个密钥库设置的命令，当然你应该根据您的环境编辑值。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1562
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# create directories to hold the key files\n"
"mkdir -p /tmp/linstor-ssl\n"
"cd /tmp/linstor-ssl\n"
"mkdir alpha bravo charlie\n"
msgstr ""
"# create directories to hold the key files\n"
"mkdir -p /tmp/linstor-ssl\n"
"cd /tmp/linstor-ssl\n"
"mkdir alpha bravo charlie\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1569
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# create private keys for all nodes\n"
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore alpha/keystore.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias alpha\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Max Mustermann, OU=alpha, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"
msgstr ""
"# create private keys for all nodes\n"
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore alpha/keystore.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias alpha\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Max Mustermann, OU=alpha, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1574
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore bravo/keystore.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias bravo\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Max Mustermann, OU=bravo, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"
msgstr ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore bravo/keystore.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias bravo\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Max Mustermann, OU=bravo, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1579
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore charlie/keystore.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias charlie\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Max Mustermann, OU=charlie, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"
msgstr ""
"keytool -keyalg rsa -keysize 2048 -genkey -keystore charlie/keystore.jks\\\n"
" -storepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -alias charlie\\\n"
" -dname \"CN=Max Mustermann, OU=charlie, O=Example, L=Vienna, ST=Austria, C=AT\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1584
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# import truststore certificates for alpha (needs all satellite certificates)\n"
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore bravo/keystore.jks -destkeystore alpha/certificates.jks\n"
msgstr ""
"# import truststore certificates for alpha (needs all satellite certificates)\n"
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore bravo/keystore.jks -destkeystore alpha/certificates.jks\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1588
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore charlie/keystore.jks -destkeystore alpha/certificates.jks\n"
msgstr ""
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore charlie/keystore.jks -destkeystore alpha/certificates.jks\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1593
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# import controller certificate into satellite truststores\n"
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore alpha/keystore.jks -destkeystore bravo/certificates.jks\n"
msgstr ""
"# import controller certificate into satellite truststores\n"
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore alpha/keystore.jks -destkeystore bravo/certificates.jks\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: administration-linstor.adoc:1597
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"keytool -importkeystore\\\n"
" -srcstorepass linstor -deststorepass linstor -keypass linstor\\\n"
" -srckeystore alpha/keystore.jks -destkeystore charlie/certificates.jks\n"
msgstr ""
